freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Diagnosed with breast cancer in my right breast. Covid shot was in my right arm.

Was diagnosed with breast cancer in my right breast. had my vaccine in my right arm. Small aggressive HER2 positive tumor that probably hasn't been there long according to the surgeon. When I had my second vaccine, my underarm and breast really hurt
